WEBVTT

00:10:29.982 --> 00:10:31.886
haven't valued education.

00:10:32.553 --> 00:10:35.612
It's because of hard history.

00:10:36.506 --> 00:10:38.467
So when I think about the past,

00:10:38.491 --> 00:10:41.426
my concern about not remembering it

00:10:41.450 --> 00:10:45.654
is not that we will repeat it
if we don't remember it.

00:10:46.242 --> 00:10:50.329
My concern, my fear
is that if we don't remember the past,

00:10:50.353 --> 00:10:52.559
we will continue it.

00:10:53.186 --> 00:10:55.537
We will continue to do the things

00:10:55.561 --> 00:11:00.119
that created inequality and injustice
in the first place.